    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single gap in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is accepted given the standardized single-condition nature of ASTM F1717 and regulatory precedent. All three primary QoIs satisfy the pre-established acceptance bounds (<10% difference, E/uval <1.96). The FEA modeling framework is accepted as adequately credible for the stated COU.",
